先減肥，唔好屈就自己係一個會因為外在因素而嫌棄你既人身邊。"},{"pid":"22511858c31486969fd3e12889d2fcc525f52609","tid":336194,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你男朋友係咪排骨黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲肉地先好啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識貨</blockquote><br />\n180 150磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家喺佢面前完全唔想除衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb0c9b8800267c927308d3bcf273160d4061bfd","tid":336194,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"110磅都肥? 仲要26腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fd6bc75f51e4a8a2ce09c609b830d2c2b13223","tid":336194,"uid":127799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:58:44.000Z","msg":"收兵post 連登仔個個話肉感 排隊入伍"},{"pid":"c34b70a23df417db7b59783c6b532665e287754a","tid":336194,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>160 50kg 其實真係好肥 最慘係你男朋友望住你會一路肥</blockquote><br />\n冇錯 本身冇拍拖 係呵冇人煮 全日訓 肥得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家拍咗拖  會車我去食飯 一日肥過一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1abcac83b5b0a85c42cd13317b1318c97fb00a0","tid":336194,"uid":130706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"我都係講下笑姐 對唔住bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbe400b773bd989d81d7f94a53d6da8f0693420","tid":336194,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:05:36.000Z","msg":"就係你男友哩類人攪到香港女仔減到又瘦又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b539d0ef3eadc780812a072b28efe3982de03d94","tid":336194,"uid":59465,"like":