gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日覺得拍拖最美好嘅係成日都會想令大家進步<br />\n其實就算佢唔講我都想減 夏天好攞命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未去到嫌棄嘅 但係 而家見到佢有時佢想攬下我都有少少自卑"},{"pid":"df974a06d23f1fecc953ed5a090eae97a08539b0","tid":336194,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>110磅都肥? 仲要26腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐喺度36<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814ef9bf35ce25dca4dc397e5805e52830df827a","tid":336194,"uid":107461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5893f589b1c8379fb66e7d582721ea09c9493ced","tid":336194,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收兵post 連登仔個個話肉感 排隊入伍</blockquote><br />\n說穿了 其實屌就肉感 帶出街就骨感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b710f72dfeb1be3acc7706f0adddf4fd56ecd3","tid":336194,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係講下笑姐 對唔住bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑笑笑好好笑呀 dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b145f6a575c6edf9bb229fae81607a40f3f7b4aa","tid":336194,"uid":114722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係你男友哩類人攪到香港女仔減到又瘦又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有陣時同佢行街喺條街度見到佢指住個瘦過自己好多既女仔係咁話肥 我都啞撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港女仔已經好撚瘦"},{"pid":"0a7c9b99f1ff880d03b5ee6027d633b444f589c2","tid":336194,"uid":124986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"160 50kg邊忽肥呀。。。<br /